text: Richard M. Murphy (born December 16, 1942) is a former American politician and lawyer. He was the 33rd mayor of San Diego, California from 2000 to 2005. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Mayors of San Diego Category:American judges Category:Politicians from Oak Park, Illinois Category:Lawyers from Illinois Category:Lawyers from San Diego Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
